      "lines": [
        "想象你刚搬到一个新街区，想找一家好吃的餐厅。",
        "你会怎么做？"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "nearest_neighbor_classifier"
      ],
      "id": "s002",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "nearest_neighbor_classifier"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "你可能会问几个邻居，看看他们平时去哪家。",
        "这就是 <term id=\"nearest_neighbor_classifier\">最近邻分类器</term> 的核心思路。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s003",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "对于一个没有标签的新数据点，",
        "我们去找训练集中和它最相似的几个点。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s004",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "然后，用这些“邻居”的标签来推断新点的标签。",
        "就这么简单。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "distance_measure"
      ],
      "id": "s005",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "distance_measure"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "要实现这个想法，我们需要三样东西：",
        "一组带标签的记录、一个 <term id=\"distance_measure\">距离度量</term>、以及 k 的值。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "k_nearest_neighbors"
      ],
      "id": "s006",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "k_nearest_neighbors"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "k 就是你想问多少个邻居。",
        "这个 k 就是 <term id=\"k_nearest_neighbors\">k 个最近邻</term> 中的 k。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s007",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "分类一个未知记录时，先计算它与其他所有已知记录的距离。",
        "然后找出距离最近的 k 个邻居。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "majority_vote"
      ],
      "id": "s008",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "majority_vote"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "最后，用这些邻居的类别标签来决定新记录的类别。",
        "最常见的方式是 <term id=\"majority_vote\">多数投票</term>。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "exercise": {
        "answer": 0,
        "explanation": "多数投票：猫出现 2 次，狗出现 1 次，所以新样本被分类为猫。",
